923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b2d567aee3485f4c5eac3a51fd963ada6be064","tid":250131,"uid":9607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主冇再上水</blockquote><br />\n開緊會被炒中"},{"pid":"8af206c58d2cd308ea3601a5fcb380ee8cfb1ccc","tid":250131,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:14:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快點上水"},{"pid":"f19122c0300ecd6246a548258323b943bb08e960","tid":250131,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:21:45.000Z","msg":"rip."},{"pid":"61202374b2bb5d64d401a16ca7a1716b5064a021","tid":250131,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做得sales manager 都要上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常唔係top sales都係身經百戰, 上黎小學雞世界問, 一係戇鳩一係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我只係30歲, 三大grad, 我由engineer做起, 然後轉轉下做左D product marketing果邊。見工時, 呢間公司個原本的舊VP好賞識我, 結果請左我做sales manager。不過前排舊VP resign, 自己創業, 所以就請左新VP。</blockquote><br />\n如果俾人炒既話，咪去舊VP到撈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd89522af2e4899969365e718144ba34bd86e79","tid":250131,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實你間公司有幾個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">multinational</span>, 但HK office唔係好多人, 幾十個左右。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nInternational 咪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e302578fa3bd07f41213ebdf291a15ef025f32","tid":250131,"uid":21593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你間公司有幾個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">multinational</span>, 但HK office唔係好多人, 幾十個左右。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nInternational 咪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMultinational company 同 international company係有分別，唔好衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56045e6a486838a885c8cd2cd18cd3bac9ad57e","tid":250131,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實你間公司有幾個人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">multinational</span>, 但HK office唔係好多人, 幾十個左右。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nInternational 咪得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMultinational company 同 international company係有分別，唔好衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMNC都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係中學雞"},{"pid":"6dd347d5db13f45b195997a62f3498c871b4d357","tid":250131,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"射波先 以後一聽到約你開呢個會就請假"},{"pid":"8b94417f95c62de6f82fd5e5ad921cbb91c9c761","tid":250131,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T08:09:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>射波先 以後一聽到約你開呢個會就請假</blockquote><br />\n避得到幾耐？<br />\n到時如果知道你特登避席嘅話，咁仲簡單，一見你返工就炒，再絕啲嘅一個電話通知話你被炒，叫你返公司執嘢走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74abb0ca98502e98bd8eb590cfe7718cc02dc306","tid":250131,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>射波先 以後一聽到約你開呢個會就請假</blockquote><br />\n避得到幾耐？<br />\n到時如果知道你特登避席嘅話，咁仲簡單，一見你返工就炒，再絕啲嘅一個電話通知話你被炒，叫你返公司執嘢走。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n使乜返公司執嘢<br />\n搵人幫你執返私人物品再速遞返就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd9e0fbbefd837eaf45bcaefd59a2b914dfeb49","tid":250131,"uid":62598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"上水啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ca01eaa026f6ef6661d6762320f6aa7fd31e39","tid":250131,"uid":35931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:05:34.000Z","msg":"樓主去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9867ac71511641ba280f8a5eea9c5d6c2e46ce16","tid":250131,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   陰公,  被人炒完 連連登都無 mood 上,  駛唔駛睇到咁重要呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b8e6140cb446e00679ca62e102d40dfdf03691","tid":250131,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做得sales manager 都要上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常唔係top sales都係身經百戰, 上黎小學雞世界問, 一係戇鳩一係假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我只係30歲, 三大grad, 我由engineer做起, 然後轉轉下做左D product marketing果邊。見工時, 呢間公司個原本的舊VP好賞識我, 結果請左我做sales manager。不過前排舊VP resign, 自己創業, 所以就請左新VP。</blockquote><br />\n如果俾人炒既話，咪去舊VP到撈囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個冇工番窮到要訓街既人<br />\n教人地點撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔掂叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea40e46e2b97e2d249c5a209cd9320b36e877d5","tid":250131,"uid":43717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:28:29.000Z","